The '''InterGalactic Currency Exchange System''' managed currency distributed by the [[InterGalactic Banking Clan/Legends|InterGalactic Banking Clan]]. The IGCES also allowed the banking clan to register new currencies. The company also streamlined the process of adding new currencies considerably, from two [[Standard year/Legends|years]], to thirty minutes.<ref name="Hnn-Currency Upheavals Deliver Profits to IBC">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|47|business/13314_1.html|Currency Upheavals Deliver Profits to IBC}}</ref>

